'''烏龜怪方蟹'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|''Xenograpsus testudinatus''}}）是[[十足目|十足目]][[短尾下目|短尾下目]]（[[螃蟹|螃蟹]]）[[怪方蟹科|怪方蟹科]][[怪方蟹屬|怪方蟹屬]]三個物種之一。

烏龜怪方蟹是一種生活在海底火山高溫溫泉週邊的特有生物，個體間不具有領域防禦行為，棲息在硫磺礦的縫隙間，或是高溫水「旁」的正常水溫中，常因此被誤認為具有耐高溫特性，實是嚴重誤解。以被海底高熱噴泉燙死的浮游生物為食<ref>{{cite news |author=廖雅欣 |title=龜山島特有蟹 住海底火山旁 |url=http://udn.com/NEWS/NATIONAL/NAT5/8192391.shtml |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131002050655/http://udn.com/NEWS/NATIONAL/NAT5/8192391.shtml |publisher=[[聯合報|聯合報]] |date=2013-09-29 |archivedate=2013-10-02 |language=zh-hant |accessdate=2013-12-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/13/11/30/n4023219.htm |title=烏龜怪方蟹 海底溫泉特有生物 |author=林恆立 |language=zh-hant |date=2013-11-30 |accessdate=2013-12-05 |archive-date=2020-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919221614/https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/13/11/30/n4023219.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.ettoday.net/news/20131002/277117.htm#ixzz3BCQMJh6L|title=熱鍋邊的螃蟹！龜山島「烏龜怪方蟹」住140℃溫泉裡|publisher=[[ETtoday|ETtoday]]生活新聞|language=zh-hant|date=2013-01-02|accessdate=2014-08-23|archive-date=2020-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919161645/https://www.ettoday.net/news/20131002/277117.htm#ixzz3BCQMJh6L|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 生物學 ==
